WEBVTT

00:02:57.516 --> 00:03:00.022
He is a housepainter by trade

00:03:00.046 --> 00:03:03.919
and someone who believes deeply
in equal rights for women.

00:03:03.943 --> 00:03:07.677
When ISIS invaded
northern Iraq where he lives,

00:03:07.701 --> 00:03:10.601
he worked with a local
women's organization

00:03:10.625 --> 00:03:13.880
to help build an underground railroad,

00:03:13.904 --> 00:03:16.156
an escape network
for women's rights activists

00:03:16.180 --> 00:03:19.555
and LGBTIQ folks who were targeted
with assassination.

00:03:19.579 --> 00:03:23.284
